article.description: — Jordan Hairston hit six 3-pointers and scored 24 to propel Howard to an 85-66 victory over Delaware State on Monday night.
article.headline: Hairston sparks Howard to 85-66 victory over Delaware State
article.linkText: Hairston sparks Howard to 85-66 victory over Delaware State
article.story: WASHINGTON -- — Jordan Hairston hit six 3-pointers and scored 24 to propel Howard to an 85-66 victory over Delaware State on Monday night. Hairston shot 9 for 14, including 6 for 9 from beyond the arc for the Bison (15-15, 9-4 Mid-Eastern Athletic Conference). Bryce Harris added 23 points and eight rebounds. Shy Odom scored 15 on 5-for-7 shooting. The Hornets (13-16, 6-7) were led by Martez Robinson with 20 points, 10 rebounds and two steals. Jevin Muniz added 14 points and Deywilk Tavarez scored nine. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
